description:
Danny recaps this week's RHOBH & RHONY. On The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, there's more Denise/Aaron drama, a cool sculpting scene for the ages, the return of Kim Richards, and more! On The Real Housewives of New York, the women take their annual trip to The Berkshires to unwind and create chaos.


RHONY Recap: 36:32ish
